                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>What is the <trademark>jACOB</trademark> Designer?</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>The <trademark>jACOB</trademark> Designer is an
                            <trademark>Eclipse</trademark> plugin, which extends
                            <trademark>Eclipse</trademark> by the functionality to develop
                            <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application designs.</para>
                    </entry>
                </row>
                <row>
                    <entry>
                        <para>
                            <emphasis>What is a <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application design?</emphasis>
                        </para>
                    </entry>
                    <entry rowsep="1">
                        <para>A <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application consists of: </para>
                        <itemizedlist>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>A <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application design,</para>
                            </listitem>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>
                                    <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application hooks and</para>
                            </listitem>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>
                                    <trademark>jACOB</trademark> resources</para>
                            </listitem>
                        </itemizedlist>
                        <para>The <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application design describes:</para>
                        <itemizedlist>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>The data model of the <trademark>jACOB</trademark> application,</para>
                            </listitem>
                            <listitem>
                                <para>The forms</para>
                            </listitem>
                            <listitem><para>etc.</para></listitem>
                        </itemizedlist>
                        <para>Describe that jACOB application design can be found in application.jad file....</para>
